# VibeCraft — Fighter 3-D Model (Wavefront OBJ)
#
# Human knight warrior with organic, natural proportions.
# Stylized low-poly aesthetic with smooth flowing forms
# that read as human, not robotic.
#
# Dimensions  : ~2.0 units tall, centred at origin
# Poly count  : ~200 triangles  
# Convention  : Y-up, right-handed coordinate system
#
# Design notes:
#   - Organic curves, not geometric octagons
#   - Natural body taper and flow
#   - Heroic but human proportions
#   - Dynamic battle-ready stance

